==English==
===Noun===
'''y-axis''' ''or'' '''''y''-axis'''

#{{alggeom}}: The axis on a [[graph]] that is usually drawn from bottom to top and usually shows the range of values of [[variable]] dependent on one other variable, or the second of two [[independent variable]]s.

